start: registered=0 unloaded=0 live=0
even 10 = true, even 7 = false
after keep_even: registered=1 unloaded=0 live=1
after Gc.compact (even held): registered=1 unloaded=0 live=1
aaa 0 5 = 5
aaa 3 1 = 6
after keep_aaa: registered=2 unloaded=0 live=2
after Gc.compact (both held): registered=2 unloaded=0 live=2
after release even + Gc.compact: registered=2 unloaded=1 live=1
after release aaa + Gc.compact: registered=2 unloaded=2 live=0
